NK010(tha)010:1: dam can lcam dral gyi mchod bskul bzhugs /
NK010(tha)010:2: dpal chen he ru ka la na mo /
NK010(tha)010:3: 'dir phur pa'i dam can mchod pa ni /
NK010(tha)010:4: gtor ma dang so so'i mthun rdzas /
NK010(tha)010:6: sman phud bzang po bshams la /
NK010(tha)010:7: bdag nyid yi dam lha'i bskyed rim dang ldan pas /
NK010(tha)010:9: phur pa'i srung ma dam tshig can //
NK010(tha)010:10: srid pa gsum gyi ph+y+wa chen po //
NK010(tha)010:11: te le yab yum rol pa'i sras //
NK010(tha)010:12: lcags kyi spyang mo mgo dgu dang //
NK010(tha)010:13: lcags kyi khyi mo mtshal mig can //
NK010(tha)010:14: zangs kyi wa mo rkang gsum ma //
NK010(tha)010:15: gser gyi 'phar ba lce brgyad la //
NK010(tha)010:16: rang rang mgo can bud med zhon //
NK010(tha)010:17: phyag na phur pa lcags kyu bsnams //
NK010(tha)010:18: rol du khyi spyang 'phar ba khrid //
NK010(tha)010:19: wa mo ngar skad lhangs se lhang //
NK010(tha)010:20: ming po shel ging dkar po ste //
NK010(tha)010:21: phyag na snying dang phur pa bsnams //
NK010(tha)010:22: ri rab zom la gnas bcas shing //
NK010(tha)010:23: dug mtsho mer ba'i klong na 'phyo //
NK010(tha)010:24: dung mkhar dkar po'i nang shed nas //
NK010(tha)010:25: shwa na'i ma tshogs dam la 'du //
NK010(tha)010:26: sha khrag gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK010(tha)010:27: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK010(tha)010:29: bdud kyi yum la gshin rje'i lcam //
NK010(tha)010:30: 'dod pa khams kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK010(tha)010:31: dpal ldan nag mo re ma ti //
NK010(tha)010:32: chibs su dre'u rta rkang gsum chibs //
NK010(tha)010:33: g.yas pa dug gi phur pa gdengs //
NK010(tha)010:34: g.yon pa bdud kyi khram bam bsnams //
NK010(tha)010:35: dpal ldan nag mo re ma du //
NK010(tha)010:36: chibs su bya rgyal khyung la chibs //
NK010(tha)010:37: g.yas pa mchog gi phur pa 'dril //
NK010(tha)010:38: g.yon pa 'dzin byed lcags kyu bsnams //
NK010(tha)010:39: dpal ldan nag mo re ma dza //
NK010(tha)010:40: chibs su sha ba yum mo chibs //
NK010(tha)010:41: g.yas pa seng ldeng phur pa bsnams //
NK010(tha)010:42: g.yon pas stong khams khram la 'debs //
NK010(tha)010:43: dpal ldan nag mo re ma dzu //
NK010(tha)010:44: chibs su chu glang sngon mo chibs //
NK010(tha)010:45: g.yas pa lcags kyi phur pa gdengs //
NK010(tha)010:46: g.yon pa 'dzin byed lcags kyu bsnams //
NK010(tha)010:47: nam zla dus bzhi'i bdag mo mdzad //
NK010(tha)010:48: 'jig rten khams kyi nad bdag mo //
NK010(tha)010:49: zhing lpags rlon pa'i na bza' can //
NK010(tha)010:50: ming po ma h+aa k+aa la ste //
NK010(tha)010:51: be con phur bu 'jol ber gsol //
NK010(tha)010:52: sku mdog nag po 'bar ba'i gdong //
NK010(tha)010:53: ri rab nag po'i byang shar mtshams //
NK010(tha)010:54: mu le ding gi lcags mkhar nas //
NK010(tha)010:55: nag mo chen mo dam la 'du //
NK010(tha)010:56: sha khrag gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK010(tha)010:57: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK010(tha)010:59: gnod sbyin zangs mdog rgyal po che //
NK010(tha)010:60: yab yum rol pa'i sras mchog ni //
NK010(tha)010:61: de byin gza' yi bu mo ser //
NK010(tha)010:62: chibs su gza' rta 'ur pa chibs //
NK010(tha)010:63: sku la ber chen ser nag gsol //
NK010(tha)010:64: phyag na phur pa lcags kyu bsnams //
NK010(tha)010:65: bse byin btsan gyi bu mo ni //
NK010(tha)010:66: dmar nag btsan rta dmar po chibs //
NK010(tha)010:67: sku la ber chen dmar nag gsol //
NK010(tha)010:68: phyag na phur pa lcags kyu bsnams //
NK010(tha)010:69: phag byin klu yi bu mo sngo //
NK010(tha)010:70: chibs su klu rta ljang sngon chibs //
NK010(tha)010:71: 'jol ber sngo khra sbrul gyis brgyan //
NK010(tha)010:72: phyag na phur pa lcags kyu bsnams //
NK010(tha)010:73: ya byin bdud kyi bu mo nag /
NK010(tha)010:74: sku la mthing nag ber chen gsol //
NK010(tha)010:75: chibs su bdud rta nag po chibs //
NK010(tha)010:76: phyag na phur pa lcags kyu bsnams //
NK010(tha)010:77: blon mo yang blon tshogs dang bcas //
NK010(tha)010:78: ming po bse yi skyes bu ni //
NK010(tha)010:79: sku la bse yi khrab chen gsol //
NK010(tha)010:80: bse mda' bse gzhu phur pa 'dril //
NK010(tha)010:81: kun kyang shan pa pho mo 'gyed //
NK010(tha)010:82: ri rab chen po'i lho nub mtshams //
NK010(tha)010:83: bse mtsho mer ba'i nang shed na //
NK010(tha)010:84: bse mkhar smug po'i pho brang nas //
NK010(tha)010:85: sa bdag chen mo dam la 'du //
NK010(tha)010:86: sha khrag gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK010(tha)010:87: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK010(tha)010:89: rdo rje gar gyi dbang phyug ma //
NK010(tha)010:90: rdo rje gsal ba glog byin ma //
NK010(tha)010:91: rdo rje kun bzang mthun mo che //
NK010(tha)010:92: rdo rje ye shes chen mo ma //
NK010(tha)010:94: rdo rje gsung dbyangs sgrog pa mo //
NK010(tha)010:95: rdo rje sgrol ma za byed ma //
NK010(tha)010:96: ma bdun sku mdog dmar nag la //
NK010(tha)010:97: rdo rje phur 'dril chas dang ldan //
NK010(tha)010:98: shar gyi rdo rje spyan gcig ma //
NK010(tha)010:99: lho yi rdo rje ral gcig ma //
NK010(tha)010:100: nub kyi rdo rje dbang sdud ma //
NK010(tha)010:101: byang gi rdo rje las mkhan mo //
NK010(tha)010:102: sring bzhi smug nag thod khrag dang //
NK010(tha)010:103: phur 'dril rang rang rgyan dang ldan //
NK010(tha)010:104: dkar ser dmar dang ljang gu'i mdog /
NK010(tha)010:105: kun kyang phur pa'i srung ma ste //
NK010(tha)010:106: de ring dpal gyi dam la 'du //
NK010(tha)010:107: bos pa'i tshe na snyan ma sra //
NK010(tha)010:108: khyod dang nga gnyis dam tshig 'brel //
NK010(tha)010:109: brten pa'i tshe na rgyang ma ring //
NK010(tha)010:110: mthun pa'i dam rdzas 'di na mchis //
NK010(tha)010:111: bskul ba'i tshe na mthu ma chung //
NK010(tha)010:112: khyod kyi srog snying nga la yod //
NK010(tha)010:113: ba ling sha khrag ri ltar spungs //
NK010(tha)010:114: mthun rdzas longs spyod gcal du bkram //
NK010(tha)010:115: glu dbyangs gdung bas khyod 'bod na //
NK010(tha)010:116: nyams pa'i dgra la mthu ma chung //
NK010(tha)010:117: brnag pa'i bgegs la rtsal ma zhan //
NK010(tha)010:118: sha khrag gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK010(tha)010:119: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK010(tha)010:120: badz+ra kro d+ha tsit+ta ma h+aa l+ai shu ra shu ra /
NK010(tha)010:123: shu la tsi p+aar shu par ni yo ga shud+d+ha tsit+ta ma ra li /
NK010(tha)010:124: kro d+ha yo gi n+ai badz+ra /
NK010(tha)010:127: zhes brjod gtor ma gtsang sar 'bul //
NK010(tha)010:128: las sbyor dus su dus drug bskul //
NK010(tha)010:129: phur bu sgrub pa'i rig 'dzin la //
NK010(tha)010:130: nye ba'i gsol ka rgyun mi bcad //
NK010(tha)010:132: nyams pa bdun gyi gshed ma yin //
NK010(tha)010:133: de bas 'di la gces par zungs //
